[^AUTHOR: BROME, RICHARD.
TEXT: A MAD COUPLE WELL MATCH'D.
IN: FIVE NEW PLAYES,
(VIZ,)
THE MADD COUPLE WELL MATCHT.
THE NOVELLA.
THE COURT BEGGER.
THE CITY WITT.
THE DAMOISELLE.
BY RICHARD BROME.
LONDON, PRINTED FOR HUMPHREY MOSELEY, RICHARD MARRIOT, AND THOMAS 
DRING, AND ARE TO BE SOLD AT THEIR SHOPS, 
1653.
