   [$ (^Sa.^) $] The Lord (^Lovely^) .
   [$ (^Car.^) $] That loves women above wine, wine above
wealth, wealth above friend, and friends above himselfe.
There's no scandall in all that sir.
   [$ (^Sa.^) $] It goes so of him indeed, but he loves honor above
